{"tid":1626430,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[撤資大法好] 平價電匯方案 - InstaRem","createTime":"2019-10-05T11:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T07:08:08.000Z","uid":258023,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"7bb98219eb66972fd8232cda6f067224fe9dda4b","tid":1626430,"uid":258023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:13:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">利申: 以下只係個人經驗</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n港共政府宣佈用緊急法去立反蒙面法, 開始咗以緊急法去繞過正常立法程序嘅先例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都怕有一日佢用緊急法黎禁止資金流動, 到時候唔單至港紙, 就連存係香港銀行嘅外幣都可能提唔翻出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />至於外幣現鈔又好難係香港用, 所以唔少巴絲建議用<span style=\"color: red;\">離岸戶口/Virtual Bank</span>撤資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁錢可以去咗外國, 但係又以簽卡嘅形式係香港到洗到用到 ( Monzo/N26/Transferwise/Revolut 等仲免手續費直接用mastercard FX rate<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">有關點開戶可以睇依道</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1596953/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1596953/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1494336/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1494336/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1335920/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1335920/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n不過問題黎啦, 到底可以點轉啲錢走呢?大路方法有二<br />\n1. 喺香港銀行開外幣account, 以銀行rate轉成外幣, 再以銀行T/T匯過去外國銀行<br />\nCost :  銀行貴rate, 香港銀行T/T手續費(~hkd60-100), 外國銀行T/T手續費(Varies from banks)<br />\n2. 喺香港以港元credit card以外幣簽帳形式張錢簽入外國銀行 (通常得Virtual Bank 用到依個方法)<br />\nCost : Credit card handling (~2%)<br />\n<br />\n以上嘅方法對於翻工巴絲可能唔覺貴, 但<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">對於翻學巴絲可能會肉赤</span></span>, 每trans一下冇幾舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係道同大家介紹一個小弟係Exchange嘅時候聽啲新加坡frd介紹嘅一個FinTech Remittance Platform - InstaRem<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d87798bd67b83b83456226e805c091b9c25f978","tid":1626430,"uid":223574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:16:49.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"67ae2a580632d1c1b09f2b1597440a62eaa4e4b7","tid":1626430,"uid":155949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:17:10.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"417863b3925a4b50cee72d2f4a73ae016b56c2fa","tid":1626430,"uid":282115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:17:56.000Z","msg":"窮撚攞現金放床下底<br />\n<br />\n［執倉］整理兵器倉庫<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625028\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625028</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"85b28fa34f233c11d1e86207754dfd32d1a6d0b2","tid":1626430,"uid":253320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:18:19.000Z","msg":"留言"},{"pid":"ddbd60ffeeb27f2f3c63d1348cc23c4d3715b567","tid":1626430,"uid":241841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:18:50.000Z","msg":"之前做過呢間公司promoter<br />\n聽啊頭講 個大老細係新加坡政府"},{"pid":"04440ae33139f4f86d8f31764fccc5f7ce93abb6","tid":1626430,"uid":67006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:20:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d9ee0f3fbc21d214bc5c685010facc6b99354ad","tid":1626430,"u