.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />難啲幫到你wor ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我以為全香港啲銀行依加已經可以免手續費㖭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:49:55.000Z","msg":"唯有開完hsbc hk premier 再搞啦<br />\n頭先check 完大新ebanking 第三者最多每日 65k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 東亞每日最多200k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nhsbc ebanking 應該多d掛<br />\n多謝分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff6335d504867153a38f0740d69a1a9bc89b15a","tid":1626430,"uid":258023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e36a010607f46ce4c4fbc4a7b3b59858e852a64f","tid":1626430,"uid":97224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:26:42.000Z","msg":"有冇同TransferWise 比較？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:52:36.000Z","msg":"小弟我正正係用Instarem去入美金去自己個Transferwise account<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#it3#do<br />\n聽落好智障<br />\n不過都係因為一個字<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">平</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nTransferwise入錢嘅話有二<br />\n1. credit card Transferwise自己要另收手續費<br />\n2. bank transfer of <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">same currency</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\noption 1 貴， option 2 係<strong>冇可能</strong><br />\n因為你要由一個海外嘅外幣戶口去匯錢，咁姐係唔係係香港都撤資啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我係用 Instarem去匯錢，用Transferwise去Keep啲錢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Instarem 唔係用黎當銀行戶口放錢，而係用黎匯錢，姐係好似街邊啲許氏兄弟啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"5c7040fa17857f5fb64059169